node.text:
Turn ‘why me’ into TRY ME. 🔥

Big news, Fam! My @MasterClass is officially out.

It’s never too late to reinvent your story and create a life you love. I know change is possible because I witness it every single day.  In my class, I’ll give you the tools to identify your purpose, discover your greatness and unleash your own superhero within. I want you to walk away from my class feeling powerful AF, with the confidence to dream bigger and the knowledge to turn your dreams into a reality. ✨

So, if you’re ready to ditch the excuses and LEVEL UP your life, click the link in my bio. 🔗

PS - @onepeloton family, for those asking about an ITH Ride... all I have to say is STAY TUNED. 😉 🤐

node.text: Year of Yes ✨ was a CELEBRATION of movement as medicine. It was so special to see our community come together for this experience. We explored gratitude, protecting your peace, setting boundaries, self-care as a form of activism, the power of saying no, and so much more. Which topic resonated with you most and how are you planning to work on it this year?

node.text: I spoke with Nicole Cardoza about Anti-Racism Daily, the newsletter she created that offers valuable information and tactical ways to take action in the fight against racism. We also discuss diversity in wellness and how we can do better. Thank you Nicole for holding space for this conversation and for the necessary work you do! 🙏🏽

node.text: This week I’m catching up with the lovely @leannehainsby all the way from the UK.  She tells me how a camel from the London Zoo became her new BFF, why the sacrifices she made during her pre-Peloton career as a professional dancer were 100% worth it, and so much more. Leanne thanks for chatting with me! I miss you and the entire UK Fam so much!

node.title: HUSTLERS AT HOME 🔥🏠 with Leanne Hainsby

Ally, thanks for chatting with me! Love you sis! 💛

TRAIN LIKE USAIN BOLT. 👟 🔥 It was such an honor to partner with the GOAT himself, @usainbolt on an epic training program, designed to help you level up your running game. 🔥

The specially curated program comprised of outdoor runs, strength classes & stretches with me, @adrianwilliamsnyc & @becsgentry is available now on @onepeloton digital. Who’s ready to start today?! Let's go, Fam! 🔥 

My classes ⬇️
20 min Int. HIIT Run 🔥 (OUTDOOR) 
20 min Adv. HIIT Run 🔥🔥 (OUTDOOR) 
20 min Int. Core Strength 💪🏽

node.text:
No such thing as the 'Sunday Scaries' tonight... my first LIVE strength class @onepeloton since returning from mat leave is tomorrow and I’ve got something special planned for y’all! ⬇️

My 20 min Pop Full Body Strength will include a FIT TEST aka an 8 min AMRAP [as many rounds as possible] comprised of 4 different foundational movements. This class will serve as your Strength Benchmark. 💪🏽

PS - This will be the same exact FIT TEST I included in my Full Body Strength classes from 8/4/2020 & 9/28/2020 in case you want to check those out and get a sneak peek of what you're in for. 😉

Bring a pen & paper 📝 so you can write down your FIT TEST score. Every time you take this class, you should aim to improve by increasing the # of reps OR by increasing your weight load. 

The hustle begins promptly at 10:45am ET.  See you there! 🔥

node.text:
EAT FEAR FOR BREAKFAST. This is what happens when you bet on yourself. 🔥

But real talk – how wild is this?! 😱 I have my very own billboard! LA Fam - If you’re driving down Sunset Blvd., you might just see a familiar face. 😉 🙋🏽‍♀️

My @masterclass launched 3 weeks ago today, and I am truly humbled by the response from everyone who has taken it so far, and the support from my incredible friends & family. 

Always remember, YOU are your greatest asset. Take my class and learn how to turn your inner critic into your inner advocate.  💪🏽 ✨

node.text:
CUBA. 🇨🇺 I come from Cuban refugees. I remember smuggling packets of powdered milk in letters to send to family still on the island growing up because the rations weren’t enough. When I visited, I saw for myself the hours people would wait for bread. My heart goes out to Cubans fighting for basic human rights. I know what my family has fought to achieve and I’m forever indebted. These photos are more than a family album. They are a link to legacy, pride, and through struggle there’s strength. 

I urge you to educate yourself on what’s been happening in Cuba, not only currently, but for decades. Spreading awareness and giving a voice to those that have been silenced can lead to real change.  #soscuba 🇨🇺

node.text:
IT STARTS WITH ONE. I believe the more people who step into the light, the world is illuminated. 🌎✨ So throw shine on someone you love. It could be someone in history, it could be a friend, a family member, someone in your community. Whoever it is, let's start to celebrate each other. 🎉 

Do it with a tweet, a comment, a text, a phone call, or a letter if you’re old school! 🤳🏽💬📞💌 

It’s through storytelling that we get out of statistic and into emotion, and into change and evolution.  That kind of shine is what the world needs right now, and always. ✨

Happy Monday, Fam! Hope y’all enjoyed your weekend! Rest & recovery are essential, and so is JOY. ✨ Don’t you dare feel guilty about it. It’s a new day, a new week, and a fresh opportunity to get after it.  Who caught my return to the Tread this morning? 🏃🏽‍♀️ 

20 min HIIT 🥵🔥+ 20 min Hip Hop Runs 🎉  are on-demand now. @onepeloton

node.text:
¡Alza la Bandera! 🇵🇷🇨🇺 We 👏🏽 did 👏🏽 that 👏🏽 Culture, Community, Legacy. ✨ Our stories are the fabric that weaves us together as one. Thank you to my parents for showing me the true meaning of resilience, grit, and hustle. 🔥 They came to this country and created themselves from nothing. That’s the legacy I plan to live up to.  Always remember where you came from. ✨

We CAN dream bigger. 💫 This play & Lin-Manuel Miranda showed me that. 🙏🏽 We don’t have to live in whatever “boxes” society puts us in. Remember that. // So @onepeloton Family, who are you paying it forward for? ⬇️ Today’s 𝘐𝘯 𝘛𝘩𝘦 𝘏𝘦𝘪𝘨𝘩𝘵𝘴 Ride is on-demand now. 💃🏽

Wepa! 💃🏽 Athena and I are ready for my 𝘐𝘯 𝘛𝘩𝘦 𝘏𝘦𝘪𝘨𝘩𝘵𝘴 Ride! ✨ See y'all on the leaderboard today at 12pm EST. 

PS - I want everyone to celebrate & rep their heritage so if you have a flag, bring it with you to the bike and wave it PROUDLY while this song plays! 🇨🇺 🇵🇷

Swagger, Reclaimed. 👑 

Damn, it feels good to be back! 🔥  Let’s start appreciating moments before they become memories. ✨ If you missed my Together We Ride live, you can catch it on-demand now.  Spoiler alert 🚨 Athena is officially part of the @onepeloton Fam! 🥰

👑 DON'T CALL IT A COMEBACK. 👑

Today is the day! I’m back on the bike tonight at 5pm ET. It’s only fitting my first Live class back is a 30 min Together We Ride. ✨ The last time I taught one of these rides was almost a year ago, when I announced I was expecting Athena. 🥰 Time flies, y’all! I cannot wait to see you all on the leaderboard. It's been a minute!! Let’s goooo! 🔥
